# Excluded derived artifacts — these are rebuilt automatically by `ticket scan --reindex`
# Only .ticket/tickets/**/ticket.toml and .ticket/tickets/**/description.md should be tracked.

# redb binary index (derived from ticket.toml files on disk)
tickets.redb
tickets.redb.lock

# Tantivy full-text search index (derived; rebuilt by scan --reindex)
search_index/

# Per-ticket advisory lock files (ephemeral, process-local)
**/.ticket-lock
